  <div class="pane-content">
    <h1 id="page-title">
	privacy and cookie policy</h1>
  </div>

  
  </div>
<div class="panel-pane pane-node-body body-block"   class="panel-pane pane-node-body body-block">
  
      
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><ul style="margin: 0.75em 0px 20px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 1.2em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.648px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Calibri, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">Who we are</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">Our promise to you</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">Why we collect your data</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">What type of data do we collect about you</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">Lawful basis for processing your data?</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">Marketing and fundraising</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">Third Party data</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">Website users and Cookies</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">What we do with your personal information</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">Keeping your data</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">Your rights</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">Sharing your story</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">Helpline Policy</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.75em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font: inherit; position: relative;">Complaints, compliments or comments</li>
</ul><p style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.648px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: Calibri, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">This website privacy policy aims to help you to understand what information Epilepsy Society might collect and process about you. Epilepsy Society is committed to protecting and respecting your privacy. Any information provided helps us to develop a better understanding of our supporters through their personal data and allows us to operate more efficiently, which ultimately helps us create a full life for everyone affected by epilepsy.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.648px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: Calibri, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">We ensure that we use your information in accordance with all applicable laws concerning the protection of personal information. This policy explains:</p>
</div>
