  <div class="content">
    <div class="expandable-rows__item expandable-row"><h2 class="expandable-row__title"><div class="field field-name-field-row-title field-type-text field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even">Third Party data</div>
      </div>
</div>
</h2><div class="field field-name-field-row-text field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even"><p>Our information may be shared with us by independent platforms, for example fundraising sites like Just Giving, PayPal or Virgin Money Giving.  These independent third parties will only do so when you have indicated that you wish to support Epilepsy Society and with your consent. You should check their Privacy Policy when you provide your information to understand fully how they will process your data.</p>
</div>
      </div>
</div>
</div>  </div>
</div>
